<h1 id="one-way-you-cant-display-canada">One Way You Canâ€™t Display Canada</h1>

<p>One final step!  Re-open the <strong>Vancouver UTM Z10</strong> map and add the <strong>CAN_WGS1984</strong> layer, then zoom to the layer extent.  Think about why this coordinate system canâ€™t display the whole country.  Try adding the other Canada layers (eg. <strong>CAN_albersEA</strong>) to see if that fixes things.  See the video below for guidance.</p>

